    <item>
      <title>开始新的一天你需要知道的五件事：美洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-07-09/five-things-you-need-to-know-to-start-your-day-americas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[早上好。投资者在等待美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的证词时保持乐观，花旗集团表示对人工智能获利了结，总统乔·拜登的战斗仍在继续。以下是推动市场的因素。—  克里斯汀·阿基诺]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-07-09/five-things-you-need-to-know-to-start-your-day-americas</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:33:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗宾汉协会称，今年美联储将降息一次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/robinhood-s-guild-will-get-one-fed-rate-cut-this-year-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Robinhood 投资策略主管 Stephanie Guild 表示，美联储今年将降息一次，这将有助于释放租赁市场需求，冷却房地产市场并降低通胀。她在彭博简报中与 Dani Burger 和 Manus Cranny 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/robinhood-s-guild-will-get-one-fed-rate-cut-this-year-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:13:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国小企业乐观情绪连续第三个月上升至 2024 年高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/us-small-business-optimism-rises-for-third-month-to-2024-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于企业对经济前景的悲观情绪有所减弱，美国小企业乐观情绪在 6 月份连续第三个月上升，达到今年的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/us-small-business-optimism-rises-for-third-month-to-2024-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曼氏集团的科尔表示，市场有望实现软着陆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/markets-assured-of-soft-landing-says-man-group-s-cole-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Man Group 多策略股票主管 Edward Cole 表示，市场似乎肯定会实现软着陆，但我们正在进入一个季节性的市场困难时期。他补充说，他不同意不拥有一家公司可以决定你全年的回报这一观点，因为对于选股者来说，有很多广泛的机会。他在彭博简报上与 Dani Burger 和 Manus Cranny 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/markets-assured-of-soft-landing-says-man-group-s-cole-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:48:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票前对冲基金押注英镑走强创六年来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/hedge-funds-piled-into-bets-for-stronger-pound-before-uk-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周英国大选前，对冲基金对英镑走强的押注飙升至六年多来的最高水平，因为投资者相信工党的胜利将给该国的政治和经济带来稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/hedge-funds-piled-into-bets-for-stronger-pound-before-uk-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:39:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃利奥特称伦敦金属交易所未能披露镍案文件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/elliott-says-lme-failed-to-disclose-key-documents-in-nickel-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对冲基金埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 就 2022 年镍危机再次与伦敦金属交易所 (LME) 展开法律斗争，称该交易所未能披露关键文件来表明其如何应对失控的空头挤压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/elliott-says-lme-failed-to-disclose-key-documents-in-nickel-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:35:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长帕内塔淡化服务业通胀高企的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/ecb-s-panetta-plays-down-concerns-about-high-services-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员法比奥·帕内塔表示，欧洲央行不应过度担心顽固的服务业通胀和依然强劲的工资增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/ecb-s-panetta-plays-down-concerns-about-high-services-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 08:47:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>淡马锡中国投资十年来首次落后于美洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/temasek-china-bets-fall-below-americas-for-first-time-in-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[淡马锡控股私人有限公司在中国的投资规模至少十年来首次低于在美洲的投资规模，凸显出全球基金经理对亚洲最大经济体的一贯谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/temasek-china-bets-fall-below-americas-for-first-time-in-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 07:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着焦点从飓风转向美联储，油价小幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-9</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国原油中心休斯顿度过风暴贝丽尔的最严重时期，以及交易员期待美联储主席杰罗姆鲍威尔为期两天的货币政策证词，油价有所下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-9</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 23:21:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔上任前美国股市或再试新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者等待美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔向国会作证以寻找美国利率前景的线索，美国股市周二有望再创历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 22:32:57 GMT</pubDate>
